f(n,m)=\sum_{k=0}^m g(n,k)=\sum_{k=0}^m\binom{k+n+1}{n}=\binom{n+1}{n}+\cdots+\binom{n+m+1}{n}
f(n,m)=\binom{n+m+2}{n+1}-\binom{n}{n}=\binom{n+m+2}{n+1}-1.
